edu.umd.cs.psl.reasoner.bool

Class BooleanMCSat

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umd.cs.psl.application.groundkernelstore.MemoryGroundKernelStore
      • edu.umd.cs.psl.reasoner.bool.BooleanMCSat
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GroundKernelStore, Reasoner

    public class BooleanMCSat
extends MemoryGroundKernelStore
implements Reasoner
    Implementation of MC-Sat, which approximates the marginal probability that each atom has value 1 in a Boolean domain.

    Marginal probabilities will be set as the atoms' truth values.

    This class supports free RandomVariableAtoms and RandomVariableAtoms that are each constrained by a single GroundDomainRangeConstraint. It also assumes that all ObservedAtoms have Boolean truth values. Its behavior is not defined otherwise.
